data.description: Move-in Ready 3 bedroom, 1 bathroom villa style condo with inviting sunroom, vaulted ceilings and lots of natural light in centrally located Cloverplace Condos. This premium location offers privacy of the wooded preserve with frequent visits from deer and area wildlife and ample green space. The spacious master suite is located facing the preserve and has access to the sunroom, offers a walk-in closet that could easily be converted to a second bathroom, plus a second closet. The A/C and roof were replaced in 2020 and the ducts were professionally cleaned in 2023. The garage was converted to a third bedroom in 2022 and is adjacent to the laundry room and kitchen. Newer water heater and bathroom features updated walk-in shower and vanity.?This quaint home is minutes from area beaches, shopping, restaurants, medical care and airports. Maintenance free living in this Florida paradise offers a community pool and extensive recent upgrades, including newly paved private roads, new siding and faux stack stone on all villa exteriors which adds to the charm and curb appeal. Maintenance fee covers essential utilities, including water, sewer, trash. Ample guest parking is also available. This is a must see!
